message.de_DE: Los, Fräulein Lea, schnappen Sie sie!
message.ja_JP: レアさん、捕まえるんだ！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/09]

message.en_US: There must be more ahead, but there's too much traffic!
message.pt_BR: Deve haver mais à frente, mas há muito tráfego!
message.de_DE: Da vorne müssen noch mehr sein, aber es ist zu viel Verkehr!
message.ja_JP: もっと先にいるな。だが車が多すぎる！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/09]
message.ko_KR: 앞에 놈들이 더 있을 텐데, 교통 체증이 심하군!<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/16]
message.zh_CN: 前面一定还有更多，但车流拥堵！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/19]

message.en_US: Ms. Lea, you need to go ahead! \c[3]Jump over the cars\c[0]!
message.pt_BR: Srta. Lea, você precisa ir em frente! \c[3]Salte por cima dos carros\c[0]!
message.de_DE: Fräulein Lea, Sie müssen vorangehen! \c[3]Springen Sie über die Autos\c[0]!
message.ja_JP:
レアさん、先に行ってくれ！
\c[3]車を跳び越えるんだ\c[0]！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/09]
message.ko_KR: 레아 양, 앞으로 가! \c[3]차 위로 뛰어서\c[0]!<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/16]
message.zh_CN: 莉亚小姐，你自己前进吧！\c[3]从车顶上跳过去\c[0]！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/19]

message.en_US: Great work, Ms. Lea!\. But we need to \c[3]go further\c[0], still!
message.pt_BR: Ótimo trabalho, Srta. Lea!\. Mas precisamos ir mais longe ainda!
message.de_DE: Gute Arbeit, Fräulein Lea!\. Aber wir müssen noch weiter nach vorn!
message.ja_JP:
レアさん、やったな！\.だが
まだ\c[3]先にも\c[0]いるぞ！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/09]
message.ko_KR: 잘했어, 레아 양!\. 하지만 아직 \c[3]더 가야 해\c[0]!<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/16]
message.zh_CN: 干得漂亮，莉亚小姐！\.但我们还能\c[3]更进一步\c[0]！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/19]

message.en_US: I will follow as soon as I get through the traffic!
message.pt_BR: Seguirei você assim que atravessar o trânsito!
message.de_DE: Ich komme nach, sobald ich durch den Verkehr durch bin!
message.ja_JP: この渋滞を抜け次第、私も後を追う！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/09]
message.ko_KR: 나도 이 체증을 뚫고 곧 뒤따라가지!<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/16]
message.zh_CN: 我穿过拥堵之后就跟上来！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/19]

message.en_US: We're getting close to their leader!\. Ms. Lea, jump on!
message.pt_BR: Estamos nos aproximando do líder deles!\. Srta. Lea, pule em frente!
message.de_DE: Wir nähern uns ihrem Anführer!\. Fräulein Lea, springen Sie auf!
message.ja_JP:
ヤツらのリーダーに近づいている！
\.レアさん、飛び乗れ！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/09]
message.ko_KR: 놈들의 우두머리와 가까워지고 있다!\. 레아, 올라타!<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/16]
message.zh_CN: 我们接近他们的首领了！\.莉亚小姐，前进吧！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/19]
